{"tid":1775989,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"八達通唔應該罷用，應該有計劃地使用","createTime":"2019-12-09T08:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T08:11:47.000Z","uid":277157,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41684cef98db9aad2ed598f7745833d927e2c5e6","tid":1775989,"uid":277157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"點解咁講，大家記唔記得正苦有個<strong>公共交通費用補貼計劃</strong><br />\n<br />\n用佢官網個例子重溫一下佢點運作：<br />\n每月公共交通開支若超出$400，政府會為超出$400的實際公共交通開支提供百分之二十五的補貼，補貼金額以每月$300為上限。<br />\n例子 :<br />\n每月公共交通開支: $1000<br />\n扣除$400後的公共交通開支: $1000 - $400 = $600<br />\n補貼金額: $600 x 25% = $150<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換言之，當你每個月交通費係＄1000時，你得到既折扣係15％<br />\n每個人都會唔同，大家都可以根據自己既交通費計返條數。而每次使用八達通時，黨鐵都會收到2％既手續費。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以只要你條交通費係收到超過2％交通津貼，正苦都係俾緊錢出嚟！</span></span><br />\n我粗略計過，<strong>各位每個月既交通費係超過＄450既話，都係可以用八達通俾錢。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗交通費外，我就唔建議大家用八達通俾錢啦</span></span>，因為無著數既野，香港人係唔會做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個文科絲，唔知有無計錯數，有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場戰爭未完，大家要保持隊型，唔可以鬆懈！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮光歸香港</span>"},{"pid":"32b47a320774e2a7ae749c3d4877d192f4bdaa09","tid":1775989,"uid":277157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁，岩用既咪幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a1b174551b0b8c6df6b4c554706bf3162c0a42","tid":1775989,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:16:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73f6917336594779c9b13d5b0204da0bd8009a39","tid":1775989,"uid":277157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fcedbe15447256139f8c12ca2256e4bf3de73792","tid":1775989,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acc12d31d723996509b2431a93682200ded81d32","tid":1775989,"uid":146277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9988c4c1862ddd3a5bfa90c98ea0f2a914bf2d8d","tid":1775989,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37c0935a254ac4e23f78ea56f01a4b6f3340d936","tid":1775989,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"幫推 所以我仲用緊"},{"pid":"d64da8d12c1a8e44588f2b04fe8e968e1589aad9","tid":1775989,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"買野一定唔用<br />\n其實想搭車都罷埋，但d銀仔流轉唔切逼住用番八達通"},{"pid":"e529fc4efb0770931d7c56c45e574657feaf3e1e","tid":1775989,"uid":277157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64da8d12c1a8e44588f2b04fe8e968e1589aad9","tid":1775989,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"買野一定唔用<br />\n其實想搭車都罷埋，但d銀仔流轉唔切逼住用番八達通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"定係唔應該搭車罷，因為交通津貼可以要政府嘔錢"},{"pid":"de3788b7bf535c25240ad67910674fe8448e8b5e","tid":1775989,"uid":74882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e529fc4efb0770931d7c56c45e574657feaf3e1e","tid":1775989,"uid":277157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64da8d12c1a8e44588f2b04fe8e968e1589aad9","tid":1775989,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"買野一定唔用<br />\n其實想搭車都罷埋，但d銀仔流轉唔切逼住用番八達通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"定係唔應該搭車罷，因為交通津貼可以要政府嘔錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T08:11:47.000Z","msg":"用交通補貼啲錢捐比星火好過唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 